review_data.title: Great place, great food
review_data.content: I had a great time at Cartell. The food was delicious, I had a quesadilla and enjoyed a margarita that was divine! The place is nicely decorated, the music in the background brings some great vibes, people are welcoming and very polite. Service was exceptional....More
